Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊~ 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 振作點 不要睡下去了 我們還有山要爬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不行了 日向 你就算一個人也要前進!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到達頂鋒同時女生魅力也會上升
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就一個人去變成萬人迷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷迷迷倒萬人~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.83,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,等...等一下 日向!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,0:01:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我站住 我們一起登山的那個約定呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷 開著空調睡著了...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫雪村葵 現在讀高一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前一直只有戶內愛好的我 最近也對登山有了興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在冬天的富士山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丟下我一個人跑了 日向還真無情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼萬人迷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你隨便做個夢就來抱怨這也太...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日有所見夜有所夢才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我服了我服了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 回憶中的山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快來 準備搭帳篷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是日向 算是我的青梅竹馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邀我去登山的 就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:35.71,Neta,NTP,0,0,0,,注:日本登山者把山劃為十合目, 一合目就是山腳, 五合目山腰, 依此類推
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二季 新第一合目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住帳篷吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的帳篷能睡下四個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折起來的時候就顯得特別小巧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而攤開的話可是很大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 來搭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人能行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很輕鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把支架穿過套管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支架?套管?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是套管 然後將作為帳篷骨骼的支架穿過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後再來一根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把支架的尖端插在鎖環上面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後還差一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭這麼大的帳篷感覺卻意外簡單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說為什麼在日向家後院搭起了帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.67,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(496,10)}真的好大啊       對吧對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山上露營?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫上心夏和楓 四個人一起住帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 感覺很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 飯還沒做好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定下次和朋友一起去露營
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露營?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用飯盒做飯 睡在帳篷...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說和大家一起 是指和女生一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就住日向家怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話有她爸爸在 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要給別人添麻煩就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就成了在日向家後院露營了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 來打樁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 打狗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是哈巴狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.00,Neta,NTP,0,0,0,,注:小葵把peg誤認為成了pug
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,peg是指樁子 就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樁子就說樁子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向外斜一點 然後打扎實了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後把拉繩套在上面 把全體固定起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就完成了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好好搭起來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小事一樁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這樣看起來就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寬敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以放開手腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 楓姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩位是驢友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我們大一級的楓姐 她也是我們登山的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:13.62,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是寬敞呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一位是初中生心夏 女生魅力很足 是治癒系女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:19.91,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好漂亮的房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我買了晚飯的食材過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓姐 你有做過的經驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是會一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淘好米後先加水泡一泡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是用的烤肉架 開始火慢慢加 中間再燒旺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是古人用來教煮飯技巧的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算嬰兒哭了也別急揭蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果蓋子被沖起來了 就壓上板磚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就不會潽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們來做咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鍋裡燒上油 把洋蔥炒變色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變色?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後炒土豆 紅蘿蔔 最後炒肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上水 煮!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微煮一會兒 把濁汁去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等咖哩塊融化後...就完成了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上這隱藏味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會變得很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯有點煮糊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這米真香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩也做得很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過完全吃不出巧克力的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要有就不叫"隱藏味道"了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要再來份!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加這麼多蛋黃醬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算少的了 要在山上的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先在邊上找個地方放了吧 咦...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心動地向上升起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向你也真是的 不幫忙收拾一個人先跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵也快去吧 很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等...等下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都排隊等著的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在別人家泡澡還真緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒在能伸開手腳的缸裡泡澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不錯的澡堂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,極樂啊極樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓姐 不能這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸 先別下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓姐 先穿上外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈 抱歉抱歉 不小心拿出習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 冷不冷?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來挺寬敞 四個人進來還是有點擠了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向你再往那邊靠點!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山上小屋住時會有更擠的情況哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正逢登山季節 擠得像上班高峰的地鐵一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣能睡著嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都累了 所以睡得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我要做荷蘭醬 多放點黃油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下次也一起來做 火腿蛋松餅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來接龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用山名來接尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺很難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那從我開始吧 富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 剛才那個不算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,額 高尾山!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 恐山!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不對 基拉韋厄火山!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在夜深了 進入戀愛話題時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛話題?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟有四個女生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵開始吧 現在有喜歡的人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太低調了 和米田君怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是小學時候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那日向你又怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 楓姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這一手啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到夢馬郎就心跳不止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢馬郎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢馬~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉很長 看起來鬆軟軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:57.04,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,『岳人の歌』
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:57.04,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,登山者之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:10:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴隨星光的那個呼喚 從滑鎖道那裡傳來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:10:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星がふるあのコールグリセードで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"那個人會來嗎?" 嘴裡銜著花想道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,あの人はくるかしら花をくわえて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾卑斯的戀歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,アルプスの恋唄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人心跳不已  回憶起那個登山者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心ときめくよ　なつかしの岳人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個溫柔的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,やさしかのきみ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 振作點 我不會丟下你不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 我吃得太撐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別放棄啊 馬上到山頂了 兩個人都變成萬人...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 日向真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我睡不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就天亮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 你怎麼這麼早就起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我回憶起小時候 我們兩人一起看日出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從富士山上看的話 會更美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家一起住帳篷真是太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要真在山上住就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.61,Next01,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(992.4,372.4)}待!續!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.61,Next02,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(992.4,372.4)}待!續!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:07.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}ねぇ～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:14.34,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}お互いの指と指、四角を作るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.89,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}目の前の景色全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:21.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}切り取って、持ってけるかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:27.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}待ってたって見事、来ない今日の日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:32.09,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}空の青、感動の輪を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:35.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}顔見合わせて笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:38.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}そう、お揃いのプレゼント
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:42.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}泣いて笑った、precious days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:46.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}10年後、100年後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:49.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}色あせない思い出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:52.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}半分持ってて、Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:07.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:14.34,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}兩人把手指比在一起 做成四角形
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}眼前全部景象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:21.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}能剪切下來 拿走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:27.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}坐立不安 期待這久久不來的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:32.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}藍藍的天 感動的圈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:35.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}看著對方的臉笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:38.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}對 禮物都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:42.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}充滿喜怒哀樂的那些特殊日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:46.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}10年後 100年後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:49.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}回憶也不會褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:52.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}兩人互持一半 Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:04.72,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 不思議、どうしてかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:12.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}君が笑うと、心の奥いつもキラリ瞬く
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:15.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will step 一歩ずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:18.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will skip 一緒にね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:30.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}気がつけば、夢中になってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:36.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}「そういう事あるよね？」って、言ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:42.00,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}ギュッと手と手繋いだら、伝わる温もり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:46.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}どこにでも、行けちゃう気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:52.87,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tin ton tan、踏み出した瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:58.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}世界がパノラマみたいに、開けたの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:03.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile どんな、空の広さ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:09.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}一人きりじゃ、きっと気付けなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:14.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 笑顔、こだましてる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:22.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}胸に広がる優しい、嬉しい、新しい予感たち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:28.44,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}一歩、一歩、進んで行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:04.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 真不可思議 為什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:12.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}你一笑起來 心裡總會閃亮亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:15.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will step 一步一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:18.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will skip 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:30.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}回過神來 發現已經著迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:36.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}"這種事會有的吧?" 你這樣說道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:42.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}緊緊地握住我的手 體溫傳達給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:46.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}不管去哪裡 都感覺無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:52.87,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tin ton tan 跨出那一步的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:58.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}世界就像全景畫一樣 展開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:03.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 無論天空有多寬闊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:09.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}如果只有我一人 肯定不會在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:14.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 笑聲迴響在耳邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:22.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}心中充滿溫柔、愉悅的感覺 還有新的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:28.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}一步 一步 前進吧
